During a recent interview, one of the Xbox big-wigs said &quot;Last time, Sony got an 18 month headstart on us with the PS2.  That will not happen again.&quot;<br>
<br>
Considering that since the Xbox is based primarily from computer hardware and can probably be developed faster than the Sony equivalent, don't expect PS3 to launch without some competition from MS on their heels.<br>
<br>
